name: Gaston HHS
tweet: Public health phone lines have been restored. If you tried to get through earlier, please try again now. If you continue to experience any issues, send us a message or email us at DHHS@gastongov.com. Thank you for your patience this morning!

name: Gaston HHS
tweet: Public health is experiencing issues with our phone system this morning: we apologize for the inconvenience and are working to resolve the issue as quickly as possible.

name: Gaston HHS
tweet: Our phone system at Summit Midwifery & High-Risk Obstetrics is currently down. We apologize for any inconvenience and are working to resolve the issue as quickly as possible. If you need to reach our staff and cannot get through, please call 704-853-5009.

name: Gaston HHS
tweet: Public Health clinics will not have late hours Thursday, January 18th and will close at 5 p.m.

name: Gaston HHS
tweet: Gaston County offices will close at 3 p.m. today and reopen at 12 noon tomorrow, January 18th.

name: Gaston HHS
tweet: While offices are currently open, we're experiencing staffing shortages due to the weather. If your appointment was rescheduled we will get you back in as soon as possible. Stay tuned for updates on early closings and please be safe out there!
